{
  "stem": "26609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Another teacher said, why do you call always [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Spieglerovna? ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Spieglerovna ?] they called her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She can do it better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Often she came up to me, that girl, and ask me how can I do that, show me that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I didn't want to make enemies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I did show her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they called out always-- they mis-- they omitted me and called out others.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that I felt it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just felt it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And other things, there were small things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But once I had to do-- and my brother, elder brother, was very proud of me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How do you say in English huta szklana?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where they blow glasses and all other things, the whole huta szklana from memory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the teacher said, the teacher would liked me said, [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Spieglerovna ?] he could do-- she could do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the other teacher said, no, no, no, there are others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Said, no, let others do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let her do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had to won a small prize.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I won a book for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I sat all night at home-- we didn't have a very big home, like here, separate bedrooms-- you know, on the floor all night.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have then electricity in Grodek.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Electricity, I remember, came much later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lwow had electricities, but not Grodek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By lamps, you know those lamps with-- and not inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You burned it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two lamps on the floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother said, go to bed, go to bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You won't be able to get up to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All night, they slept in another room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I did it in the kitchen on the floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I did the whole huta just from memory.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
